data.description:
Welcome to your dream retreat in the heart of the Pocono Mountains, nestled within the Emerald Lakes Homeowners Association. This fully furnished 3-bedroom, 2-bath, three-story property on 2.41 acres offers access to a range of amenities, including indoor and outdoor pools, boating and fishing on pristine lakes, playgrounds, a community center, and a bar and grill. Enjoy the perfect blend of luxury, nature, and community living, making this getaway an ideal destination for all seasons. One month security, utilities not included. Available immediately, multiple lease terms considered.
